Thai Translation of ESR's Articles
==================================

This project translates ESR's The Cathedral and the Bazaar series into Thai.
The series is considered the most influential one to Open Source world.

Source:
http://catb.org/~esr/writings/cathedral-bazaar/

* Build Requirements:

  - gnome-doc-utils
  - xsltproc
  - docbook-xml
  - docbook-xsl

* To generate a new PO or update existing PO for translation:

    $ make {article}.th.po

  For example, for cathedral-bazaar.xml:

    $ make cathedral-bazaar.th.po

* To generate translated HTML for a particular article:

    $ make {article}.th/index.html

* To generate all articles, translated or not:

    $ make

